odía de lunes a viernes con bebidas, aperitivos y un ambiente para socializar y discutir transporte.","description:ja":"日常的な移動サポートを提供します。馬車の貸し出し、装具の調整、24時間対応の松葉杖と杖などがあります。月曜日から金曜日まで毎日正午にドリンクや軽食を提供し、リラックスした雰囲気の中で交流や交通手段について話し合うパーティーを開催しています。","description:ru":"Ежедневная поддержка мобильности: выдача повозок, подгонка ортезов, круглосуточные костыли и трости. С понедельника по пятницу в полдень — вечеринки с напитками и общением.","description:zh":"提供每日移动支持，如马车租借、支架调整和全天候拐杖和拐杖使用。他们在周一至周五每天中午举办派对，提供饮料、小吃和轻松的氛围，供社交和讨论交通需求。","email":"goldie@burningchariots.com","end_date":"2025-09-04","name":"Chariot Project BRC","opening_hours":"Mo-Su 09:30-14:00","taxi_vehicle":"cycle_rickshaw","website":"https://burningchariots.com","website:camp_listing":"https://burningman.org/event/2025-camp-listings/?yyyy=&tcq=mobility#a1XVI000008zYsz2AE","wheelchair":"designated","wheelchair:description:en":"Offers mobility-impared, invisible handicaps, and wheelchair-accessible chariots for exploring the playa."}},"13080604872":{"location":[40.7809516,-119.2116888],"tp":"CS","tags":{"contact:email":"BRCaccessibility@Gmail.com","description":"Service camp at Burning Man providing accessible camping, mobility aids, and tours to support people with disabilities for radical inclusion.","description:en":"Service camp at Burning Man providing accessible camping, mobility aids, and tours to support people with disabilities for radical inclusion.","description:es":"Campamento de servicio en Burning Man que ofrece campamento accesible, ayudas para la movilidad y tours para apoyar a personas con discapacidades para la inclusión radical.","description:ja":"バーニングマンのサービスキャンプで、アクセシブルなキャンプ場、移動補助具、障害者のためのラジカル・インクルージョンを支援するツアーを提供。","description:ko":"버닝맨의 서비스 캠프로, 장애인을 위한 접근 가능한 캠핑, 이동 보조기구, 투어를 제공하여 급진적인 포용을 지원합니다.","description:zh":"火人节的服务营地，提供无障碍露营、行动辅助设备和支持残障人士的包容性游览。","email":"BRCaccessibility@Gmail.com","end_date":"2025-09-04","name":"Mobility Camp","website":"https://mobilitycamp.org","website:camp_listing":"https://burningman.org/event/2025-camp-listings/?yyyy=&tcq=#a1XVI000009iCLF2A2","wheelchair":"designated","wheelchair:description:en":"Mobility Camp offers accessible camping, mobility aid loans, medical equipment charging, guided playa tours, and volunteer support for Burners with disabilities."}},"13082757130":{"location":[40.7841827,-119.2115001],"tp":"CS","tags":{"addr:city":"Black Rock City","addr:housenumber":"6:45","addr:postcode":"89412","addr:state":"NV","addr:street":"Esplanade","end_date":"2025-09-04","name":"Lamplighters","opening_hours":"24/7"}}}